trans-unit.source: Represents a container for <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Visual3D"></xref> objects.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ContainerUIElement3D.Children%2A> collection of a ContainerUIElement3D element can only consist of <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> objects.
Adding a <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> child to a ContainerUIElement3D implicitly adds it to the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Visual3DCollection> for the ContainerUIElement3D element.

trans-unit.source: ContainerUIElement3D does not have a visual representation; it serves as a container for other visual 3-D objects.
trans-unit.target: ContainerUIElement3D 시각적;가 없습니다. 3 차원 다른 시각적 개체에 대 한 컨테이너로 사용 합니다.

trans-unit.source: ContainerUIElement3D is a <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> object, which provides support for input, focus, and events in 3-D.
trans-unit.target: ContainerUIElement3D는는 <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D>입력, 포커스 및 3 차원으로 이벤트에 대 한 지원을 제공 하는 개체입니다.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D>
